er til utlandet, at Zapna automatisk aktiveres.\r\n\r\n<div ><span class=\"btn3\"><a href=\"?page_id=421\">Bestill</a></span></div>','Slik fungerer','','publish','open','open','','slik-fungerer','','','2012-10-06 16:29:02','2012-10-06 16:29:02','',0,'http://localhost/mw/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(9,1,'2012-10-06 12:50:57','2012-10-06 12:50:57','','Slik fungerer','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision','','','2012-10-06 12:50:57','2012-10-06 12:50:57','',8,'http://localhost/mw/?p=9',0,'revision','',0),(10,1,'2012-10-06 12:51:22','2012-10-06 12:51:22','Zapna','Zapna','','publish','open','open','','zapna','','','2012-10-06 12:51:22','2012-10-06 12:51:22','',0,'http://localhost/mw/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(11,1,'2012-10-06 12:51:21','2012-10-06 12:51:21','','Zapna','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision','','','2012-10-06 12:51:21','2012-10-06 12:51:21','',10,'http://localhost/mw/?p=11',0,'revision','',0),(12,1,'2012-10-06 12:51:33','2012-10-06 12:51:33','<br clear=\"all\" /><strong>Oversikt over landskoder</strong><br />\r\n<p>\r\nVi gir deg full oversikt over landskoder til hele verden. Uansett vilket land du skal ringe til finner du landskoden her. Oversikten er ordnet alfabetisk og lister landskodene til 251 land og regioner verden over. Hvis du ringer mye til utlandet kan vi også tilby deg store besparelser – Med vår patenterte løsning kan du spare inntil 90 prosent på samtaler til utlandet!</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<table width=\"432\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><colgroup><col width=\"269\" /> <col width=\"163\" /> </colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"269\" height=\"20\">Land</td>\r\n<td width=\"163\">Landskode</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"269\" height=\"20\">Afghanistan</td>\r\n<td width=\"163\">93</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"269\" height=\"20\">Albania</td>\r\n<td width=\"163\">355</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"269\" height=\"20\">Algeri</td>\r\n<td width=\"163\">213</td>\r\n</t